dhṛg ity ayaṃ śuddhapāṭhaḥ | |

<commentary>yathāvat tāṃ aham adhigamya sarvasattvānāṃ yathāśayaviśeṣāt prakāśayiṣye || kimartham ity āha | tatra aśeṣakleśā iti kleśopakleśā gṛhyante teṣāṃ nāśāya | aśeṣājñānahānaya iti aśeṣeṣu padārtheṣv ajñānaṃ aśeṣājñānam aśeṣājñānahānis tadarthaṃ prakāśayiṣye ||</commentary>

evam ityādi | evam anena prakāreṇa bhagavān guhyendro vajrapāṇis tathāgatam adhyeṣya |